
  Taillow    Normal Type Pokémon

  TAILLOW courageously stands 
  its ground against foes, however 
  strong they may be.  This gutsy 
  Pokémon will remain defiant even 
  after a loss.  On the other hand, 
  it cries loudly if it becomes 
  hungry. 
